WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:03.160
Come, come, come in, hahaha, come.

2
00:00:03.160 --> 00:00:08.120
You see, this is your favorite place to play when you and that kid were kids

3
00:00:08.120 --> 00:00:11.340
That kid also said that he wants to marry you when he grows up

4
00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:12.760
He doesn't even recognize you now

5
00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:14.780
Who is he?

6
00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:17.720
Then you will know

7
00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:21.700
You see, you two used to sit there and play when you were little. Look

8
00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:41.400
Boy, you gotta take care of me

9
00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:42.660
It's with us now.

10
00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:44.420
If you want to save him

11
00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:46.180
Just bring 100 million

12
00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:47.960
What do you mean?

13
00:00:47.960 --> 00:00:51.740
I think you must have a lot of regrets that you forgot.

14
00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:53.340
I'll give it to you then.

15
00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:56.600
You are really hazy

16
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:57.560
Who is it?

17
00:00:57.560 --> 00:00:59.720
I will also send you the address where you are.

18
00:00:59.720 --> 00:01:03.260
I think this must be the person you are most familiar with

19
00:01:10.040 --> 00:01:12.200
Sir, your mother was discharged from the hospital in a car accident

20
00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:13.960
What? My mother was in an accident.

21
00:01:13.960 --> 00:01:15.540
Ok, I'll be right over.

22
00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:17.480
Brother Liu, something happened to you

23
00:01:17.480 --> 00:01:19.560
Mingchuan, let me accompany you to the hospital

24
00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:22.380
I think there must be a lot of doubts in my heart

25
00:01:22.440 --> 00:01:24.440
I'll give you the antidote one by one.

26
00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:27.080
Who are you really Mengmeng?

27
00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:28.660
No need to wait for news at home.

28
00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:40.840
Are you finished?

29
00:01:40.840 --> 00:01:42.600
Didn't I ask you to find Qin Shiyu?

30
00:01:42.600 --> 00:01:45.440
Daughter, if you don't give me 5 million

31
00:01:45.440 --> 00:01:49.340
We can let Qi Tianchuan know the truth today

